Description: Buran universal application server
 High-performance application server: static files, routing/rewrites and
 language runtimes (PHP via embed SAPI) behind one process tree with a
 static YAML configuration.

Package: buran-php
Architecture: any
Depends: buran (= ${binary:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Buran universal application server - PHP runtime module
 PHP runtime module for Buran, linked against the PHP version shipped by
 this distribution release. The module binary carries the version in its
 name (e.g. buran-php84), matching `module:` in buran.yaml one to one.
